{"tid":207400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「社會實況」每日調景嶺都上演搶櫈仔","createTime":"2017-04-19T00:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T07:35:40.000Z","uid":56667,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54a0d18aac3a7be35f3288ab6a8e3ae350a613c1","tid":207400,"uid":56667,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"我哩啲蟻民每朝從將軍澳搭地鐵返九龍塘，但每次經過調景嶺真係個人會燥。<br />\n<br />\n     落車見到對面有車，緊係飛奔過去上車，但幕門啲L樣打橫圍住道門（為左等下一班有位坐），搞到啲趕時間嘅左穿右插，你班L樣有無諗過人感受？<br />\n    <br />\n    算~今日唔趕時間，我等下一班車坐下，咁就企係幕門兩側（比啲要上車嘅人上先），Hi 真係1分鐘都唔L洗班「中間黨」又出現，塞住後面啲人，我算我心諗唔關我事唔好理咁多，點知下一班車到站班「中間黨」好似食L咗屎咁鬥撞，重演幼稚搶櫈仔。<br />\n    <br />\n    最後，我哩啲毒L唯有死死氣等多班車，我想你地反思，我理得你係蝗人定港人都應該顧下人感受，坐少陣洗死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：發現好心係無好報，要做自私的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d5d4eb37de9af6d43d51ba25583244c98c5433","tid":207400,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:50:45.000Z","msg":"收工先正 成班廢中好似跑馬咁搶閘跑去對面月台霸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a97f056269690762ace7b3ab031ea43785951f9","tid":207400,"uid":817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:51:45.000Z","msg":"早少少出去迫巴士啦"},{"pid":"abb015067e2a91bdadc84f533ff5ce825b2fc4a5","tid":207400,"uid":56667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收工先正 成班廢中好似跑馬咁搶閘跑去對面月台霸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真洗唔洗呀？香港地鐵啲站咁密，你洗企幾耐呀？<br />\n<br />\n除非你由屯門搭到寶琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72de8a5b6b875ddbc6ffbe6045c9d8008459a6bf","tid":207400,"uid":8276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收工先正 成班廢中好似跑馬咁搶閘跑去對面月台霸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n調景嶺返工<br />\n日日收工都會見到d人餓狗搶屎咁衝去黃埔架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09250ffd5d01baf843c15bb86c22d146a570517","tid":207400,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:54:24.000Z","msg":"地鐵搭lift好撚精彩<br />\n<br />\n月台架lift一到，四肢健全既阿嬋，講鄉下話，阿叔，全部一個箭步，bypass前面既輪椅人，BB車，逼哂入lift<br />\n<br />\n架lift閂門上升個下，班仆街仲要望一望出面班有需要人仕O哂咀咁入唔到lift"},{"pid":"6047841e5a2ae3c36766eed02a23fdd716b0a4a3","tid":207400,"uid":56667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早少少出去迫巴士啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳區域係荒島，過海巴士無，九龍塘無，叻在最近成功爭取咗荃灣巴士"},{"pid":"6ff06a83febf7e4bdb4e6f42b3483cea631252a3","tid":207400,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:58:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8476ccb26cf14b6d1e600dd274840f4a7e627806","tid":207400,"uid":56667,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hi你老母<br />\nL你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講屌講撚先啱你心意？唔好咁膚淺啦重點唔哩到"},{"pid":"0858caad18c7057e41c4a88f8226e2dd338dbd59","tid":207400,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:02:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"931e506a6d202b2fbda17a7ec91c52a31f733946","tid":207400,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab15decd05905eef13ec73c37b7b7299454e188b","tid":207400,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T